In re BROWNING KING & CO., Bankrupt. The PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF NEW YORK, Appellant, v. IRVING TRUST COMPANY, Appellee. No. 76. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit Nov. 4, 1935.

Before L. HAND, SWAN, and AUGUSTUS N. HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed on authority of In re Flatbush Gum Co., 73 F.(2d) 283 (C.C.A.2).
